LoadMessages(conversationId: widget.conversationId))`，而 ImLoadMessages 的 hand
ler 中：\n    ```dart\n    if (event.cursor == null) {\n      _messages.clear();
\n    }\n    ```\n    所以在首次加载时会清除。这是正确的。\n\n13. **ImBloc 的 _o
nMessageAck 中 clientMessageId 为空字符串的处理**：\n    ```dart\n    final inde
x = _messages.indexWhere(\n      (m) => m.clientMessageId == event.clientMessage
